== How to update the translations for software.o.o:

The translation files are stored in the i18n repo on berlios: 

svn co http://svn.berlios.de/svnroot/repos/opensuse-i18n/trunk/lcn/
export MY_LCN_CHECKOUT=<path to lcn files>
cd $MY_LCN_CHECKOUT && ./configure

To update the .mo files with those from the lcn repo:
rake makemo
# use git add for new files

To update the .mo files with those from the lcn repo (only those without fuzzy translations will be copied): 
rake makemo
